ner"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/how-my-childhood-demonic-doll-turned-me-into-a-lifelong-horror-fan/">How My Childhood Demonic <br>Doll Turned Me Into a <br>Lifelong Horror Fan</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">October 7, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/lauravenitagreen/">Laura Venita Green</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
